title: DataCore SANsymphony: Snapshots
agents: datacore_rest
catalog: storage/datacore
license: GPLv2
distribution: andre_eckstein
description:
 This check monitors snapshots in a DataCore SANsymphony storage system.
 Snapshots provide point-in-time copies of virtual disks for backup
 and recovery purposes.

 The check displays:

 - Total number of snapshots
 - Latest snapshot timestamp and name
 - List of the 10 most recent snapshots (in details)

 The check always returns {OK} as it is informational.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through
 "DataCore SANsymphony via REST API".

discovery:
 One service is created for the SANsymphony system.
